### Ideas:

- Dynamic portals and smart roots. Metadata on root w/ smart summary option, passable by portals. Portals as map endpoints - no user map editing past a portal (remove add button from portal radial), all dynamic subcontent (auto spawn children, dynaamic behavior from payload, pass/pull metadata etc. - based on payload root node type & metadata, etc.).

- Extract smart portal behavior into dynamic agent and prompt type systems and sub-node-types. Depreciate smart portal, all portals "smart", see above (dynamic portals).

- Link user profiles to Person system and refine that system into map-native Contacts & Communities system(social network, file sharing, and collaboration). Expand Person system into map-native Contacts system with Person, Groups/Community/Organization pages, etc., their relationships, resources (maps, assets, etc.), and connections (including map-native multi-user map editing and shared project spaces). Should be able to build and launch a community as a mapstate that links users together and has its own specialized phase engine. The simplest version of this would be a single user w/ many contacts (perhaps categorized?), viewable as a map.

